    "• Neurodiversity and cognitive load.",
    "Cognitive impairment associated with dementia can limit how much PwD can benefit from apps that place high demands on cognition (Hugo and Ganguli, 2014).",
    "Therefore, the design of supportive apps for dementia patients should account for potential cognitive deficits faced by this population by minimizing cognitive load.",
    "• Mobile phone use.",
    "The prime outlet for digital apps is mobile phones."
